{"tid":110881,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]茶記啲紙巾有乜用","createTime":"2017-02-07T04:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T05:01:29.000Z","uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27a260d480aa45fedb191a762f9fb65fb2111267","tid":110881,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"無論去邊間茶記都好 佢哋都會清一式俾呢種紙巾啲客<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/07/123535_84c2000660193869ece43666cd91523c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2F123535_84c2000660193869ece43666cd91523c.jpg&h=7eca3f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張嘢細張就不在話下<br />\n又唔吸水又唔吸油<br />\n用嚟抹嘴真係抹完同無抹一樣<br />\n究竟張嘢有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1ac89c7bf274100b07047a86ee0c4571dbdb34","tid":110881,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"有冇聽過一乾三濕?"},{"pid":"64e4b0b71e23a16cf457c16cae6d5a556c8d8a04","tid":110881,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:40:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e50e0e6413f44111a6d24b4227911efa6029076","tid":110881,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇聽過一乾三濕?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f7c7a19bd97378ed7778833beada20f1dae747","tid":110881,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:40:55.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0c3dc6e8ea91a7c8bb3cfdc79d35fd9009e802","tid":110881,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n覺得係攞黎墊枱/包住餐具 唔係攞黎抺咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae7e53876628a68756fcaa0b149649325e801da","tid":110881,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lm<br />\n覺得係攞黎墊枱/包住餐具 唔係攞黎抺咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但有啲啲餐具擺喺架 個伙記見你就食完就隨手俾一疊仔我"},{"pid":"92acf2121ecdbbb6e06ce46691487faa592a1c10","tid":110881,"uid":8619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:51:01.000Z","msg":"佢見你就食完先比你 就係想你抺乾淨啲餐具等佢唔洗洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389a89aaa3d02856c14621c9bda74e8c268753f8","tid":110881,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"春卷皮黎 攞黎包飯/餸 食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d01b04b80e1ac3affd123170ac1131d71fd385","tid":110881,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:55:25.000Z","msg":"我懷疑抆屎都抆唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83053d398e0d23565ffb8edee0456ddfc4fb28cd","tid":110881,"uid":38408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇聽過一乾三濕?</blockquote><br />\n有聽過化學狼人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d40b0f902be804b9aa55a51102e669bcd1df7ce","tid":110881,"uid":38145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇聽過一乾三濕?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n呢個係舊時廣東人o既傳統<br />\n<br />\n以前d面店講o既係「一乾三濕」<br />\n即係麵、湯、茶、汁 四樣<br />\n無論你食雲吞麵 雲吞撈麵 都一定要上齊呢四樣<br />\n如果你食撈麵 最正宗最傳統o既食法應該係先飲茶漱口<br />\n之後加醬油落兜湯度 食幾啖麵 含一啖湯<br />\n一野噴落個小二身上<br />\n「hi! 咁難食點食呀! 」<br />\n<br />\n咁個店家就知你係行家 會打番個7折比你"}]}